    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138780/extras/cc98eba0bd93b4eb04c9ac38477e183f.avif?t=1771022484\" width=616 height=190 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138780/extras/714d1d1f30463d2504bfe0b4a747bcc8.avif?t=1771022484\" width=600 height=320 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《触手回春》中，你将化身一位乡村医生，运用古老而神秘的医疗技艺，为村民诊治病痛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138780/extras/2bbe3af72e2333deb06008651315ca16.avif?t=1771022484\" width=587 height=145 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138780/extras/2998c4263daa885e31733538308d448c.poster.avif?t=1771022484\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138780/extras/2998c4263daa885e31733538308d448c.webm?t=1771022484\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138780/extras/2998c4263daa885e31733538308d448c.mp4?t=1771022484\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >恐怖的造物将不断扭曲现实，侵蚀你的理智——它们会制造幻觉、妨碍你的行动，甚至让你误信治疗结果，从而将你一步步引向深渊。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138780/extras/e5e67a5d3780fd6270c73fb77fa4f44c.avif?t=1771022484\" width=587 height=145 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138780/extras/2c323b2307c7af1cb2ce1a83f2c60869.poster.avif?t=1771022484\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138780/extras/2c323b2307c7af1cb2ce1a83f2c60869.webm?t=1771022484\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138780/extras/2c323b2307c7af1cb2ce1a83f2c60869.mp4?t=1771022484\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据隐晦的线索诊治病患。每个病例都会提供一些提示，但往往不足以揭露真相，因此你必须谨慎思考每一个决定，承担相应的风险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138780/extras/905e0ab55c2a2b8cba57826aa9fdad95.avif?t=1771022484\" width=587 height=145 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138780/extras/483f84750c2d33ffc15720b4380b7785.poster.avif?t=1771022484\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138780/extras/483f84750c2d33ffc15720b4380b7785.webm?t=1771022484\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138780/extras/483f84750c2d33ffc15720b4380b7785.mp4?t=1771022484\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >存活 30 天：承受治病救人的压力，同时在越发险恶的环境中存活 30 天。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种结局：你的选择和行动将带你走向不同的结局。试着揭哓全部 10 种结局吧。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你喜欢职业模拟游戏，或热衷于在重压之下做出关键决策，那么《触手回春》这款融合了策略与恐怖元素的游戏绝对不容错过。在谜底揭晓之前，一切都充满了悬念。</p>",
